\" <small>(featuring Aastha Gill)</small>\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Sony Music Entertainment\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Punjabi\n|\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=RayZR Mera Swag by Badshah|date=2016-06-24|url=https://www.saavn.com/s/album/punjabi/RayZR-Mera-Swag-2016/FKCmz8GFSCA_|accessdate=2017-06-28}}</ref>\n|-\n|\"Garrari Pitbull Te\" <small>(Gurinder Rai featuring Badshah)</small>\n|\n|\n|-\n|\"Driving Slow\"\n|MTV India\n| rowspan=\"17\" | Hindi\n|\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Driving Slow by Badshah|date=2016-08-17|url=https://www.saavn.com/s/album/hindi/Driving-Slow-2016/eXxX5dIz43w_|accessdate=2017-06-28}}</ref>\n|-\n|\"Move Your Body\" <small>(with [[Sean Paul]])</small>\n|[[Zee Music Company]]\n|Music by DJ Shadow Dubai\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Move Your Body by Badshah, Sean Paul|date=2016-12-20|url=https://www.saavn.com/s/album/hindi/Move-Your-Body-2016/jVIs4sTJmwM_|accessdate=2017-06-28}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2017\n|\"Pop the Bottle\" <small>(with [[Vishal\u2013Shekhar]] and Akasa Singh)</small>\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Sony Music Entertainment\n|\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Pop The Bottle by Vishal, Shekhar, Vishal Dadlani, Badshah, Akasa Singh|date=2017-03-21|url=https://www.saavn.com/s/album/hindi/Pop-the-Bottle-2017/GO4NRxib40I_|accessdate=2017-06-28}}</ref>\n|-\n|\"Mercy\"\n| Released as ONE (Original Never Ends)\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Mercy by Badshah|date=2017-04-01|url=https://www.saavn.com/s/album/hindi/Mercy-2017/hZ1INs0ds98_|accessdate=2017-06-28}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\" | 2018\n| \"KareJa\" <small>(featuring Aastha Gill)</small>\n| rowspan=\"6\" | Sony Music India\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=Kareja (Kare Ja) (feat. Aastha Gill) - Badshah Song - BBC Music |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/music/tracks/n4vr8m |website=BBC |accessdate=21 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"Buzz\" <small>(Aastha Gill featuring Badshah)</small>\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web |title=Hindi Song Buzz Remix By DJ Yogii Featuring Aastha Gill And Badshah {{!}} Entertainment - Times of India Videos |url=https://m.timesofindia.com/videos/entertainment/music/hindi/hindi-song-buzz/videoshow/64643599.cms |website=m.timesofindia.com|accessdate=21 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"Heartless\" <small>(featuring Aastha Gill)</small>\n| Released as ONE (Original Never Ends)\n|<ref>{{cite web |title=ONE (Original Never Ends) |url=https://gaana.com/album/one-original-never-ends |website=Gaana |accessdate=21 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"Nain\" <small>(featuring Aastha Gill)</small>\n|\n|\n|-\n| \"Aashiq Awaara\" <small>(featuring [[Sunidhi Chauhan]])</small>\n|\n|\n|-\n| \"[[She Move It Like]]\"\n|\n|\n|-\n| \"This Is How We Do It\" ([[Now United]] featuring Badshah)\n| [[XIX Entertainment]]\n|\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2019\n| \"Har Ghoont Mein Swag\" <small>(featuring [[Tiger Shroff]] and [[Disha Patani]])</small>\n| T-Series\n|\n|\n|-\n|\"Paagal\"\n|Sony Music India \n|\n|\n|-\n|\"Kamaal\"(Amit [[Uchana]]) <small>featuring Badshah)</small>\n|YRF\n|\n|\n|-\n|\"Are you ready for the Big Bang\" (Flipkart)\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|\"Interstellar\"\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|\"Theraphy\"\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|2020\n|\"Genda Phool\" (featuring [[Jacqueline Fernandez]] and [[Payal Dev]])\n|Sony Music India\n|\n|\n|-\n|2020\n|\"Boht Tej\" (Fotty Seven featuring Badshah)\n|Sony Music India\n|\n|\n|}\n\n=== Filmography ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n| style=\"background:#ffc;\"| \n| Denotes films that have not yet been released\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#cfc; text-align:center;\"\n|'''Year'''\n|'''Song'''\n|'''Singer(s)/co-singer(s)'''\n|'''Composer(s)'''\n|'''Label'''\n|'''Language'''\n|'''Movie'''\n|'''Reference(s)'''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2014\n|\"Saturday Saturday\"\n|[[Akriti Kakkar]], [[Indeep Bakshi]]\n|[[Sharib Sabri|Sharib]]-[[Toshi Sabri|Toshi]]\n|[[Sony Music India]]\n|rowspan=\"8\" | Hindi\n|[[Humpty Sharma Ki Dulhania]]\n|\n|-\n|Dhup Chik\n|[[Aastha Gill]], Raftaar\n|[[Raftaar (rapper)|Raftaar]]\n|rowspan=3|[[T-Series (company)|T-Series]]\n|[[Fugly (film)|Fugly]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Abhi Toh Party Shuru H